values.content:
=You are a social media assistant.  
I will provide you with structured JSON describing an image.  
Your task is to generate exactly:

1. One short, catchy caption (max 20 words).  
2. Five trending hashtags relevant to the image.  

Return only valid JSON. Do not include explanations, text outside JSON, or code fences.

Format:
{
  "caption": "your caption here",
  "hashtags": ["#tag1", "#tag2", "#tag3", "#tag4", "#tag5"]
}

Here is the image description:
objects:{{ $json.output.objects }}
subject:{{ $json.output.subject }}
Color:{{ $json.output.colors }}
background:{{ $json.output.background }}
style:{{ $json.output.style }}
mood:{{ $json.output.mood }}
possible_use_cases:{{ $json.output.possible_use_cases }}

